        get (map f t) k h' = f (t.getKey k ⋯) (get t k ⋯)

        Variant of get_map that holds without LawfulEqCmp.

        get! (map f t) k = (Option.map (f k) (get? t k)).get!

        @[simp]
        theorem Std.DTreeMap.Const.toList_map {α : Type u} {cmp : α → α → Ordering} {β : Type v} {γ : Type w} {t : DTreeMap α (fun (x : α) => β) cmp} {f : α → β → γ} :
        toList (map f t) = List.map (fun (p : α × β) => (p.fst, f p.fst p.snd)) (toList t)
